
Croma: Pioneering Consumer Electronics Retail in India
Croma is India's first large-format consumer electronics and durables retailer, founded in 2006 by the Tata Group. Known for its wide range of over 20,000 products from top brands, Croma offers a seamless shopping experience across physical stores and an online platform. The brand is committed to innovation, customer service, and providing value-for-money solutions. Croma also offers unique services like lifetime product support and express delivery. With a strong presence in India, Croma continues to lead in the retail space, combining technology and customer-centric offerings.

